body_html:
For any one who still got the problem:

TensorFlow fixed this issue in their source code from r1.5, but that comes with a new problem with graph binary version if you use older TensorFlow version to inference the model, so you have to keep using TensorFlow r1.5 or above to inference the quantized model.

body:
For any one who still got the problem:

TensorFlow fixed this issue in their source code from r1.5, but that comes with a new problem with graph binary version if you use older TensorFlow version to inference the model, so you have to keep using TensorFlow r1.5 or above to inference the quantized model.
